def setting_year_of_release(row):
    platform = row['platform']
    year_of_release = row['year_of_release']

    if pd.isna(year_of_release):
        row['year_of_release'] = int(platform_grouped[platform_grouped.index == platform]['year_of_release'][0])
    else:
        row['year_of_release'] = int(row['year_of_release'])
        
    return row

game_data = game_data.apply(setting_year_of_release,axis=1)
game_data.head()

def setting_critic_score(row):
    genre = row['genre']
    critic_score = row['critic_score']

    if pd.isna(critic_score):
        try:
            row['critic_score'] = genre_grouped[genre_grouped.index == genre]['critic_score'][0]
        except:
            pass
    
    return row

game_data = game_data.apply(setting_critic_score,axis=1)
game_data.head()

def setting_user_score(row):
    genre = row['genre']
    user_score = row['user_score']
    
    if pd.isna(user_score):
        try:
            row['user_score'] = genre_grouped_for_users[genre_grouped_for_users.index == genre]['user_score'][0]
        except:
            pass
    
    return row

game_data = game_data.apply(setting_user_score,axis=1)
game_data.head()
